    <item>
      <title>伍德赛德和桑托斯正在进行早期合并谈判，以创建液化天然气巨头</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/santos-says-it-s-in-preliminary-merger-talks-with-woodside</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伍德赛德能源集团有限公司 (Woodside Energy Group Ltd.) 正在与桑托斯有限公司 (Santos Ltd.) 就潜在合并进行初步谈判，这为在全球数十亿美元的能源交易浪潮中创建澳大利亚天然气出口巨头打开了大门。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/santos-says-it-s-in-preliminary-merger-talks-with-woodside</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 07:49:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>国家工业步履蹒跚，欧元区衰退迹象加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/german-industry-unexpectedly-shrinks-amid-recession-threat</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国和意大利的工业生产在今年最后一个季度开始出现下滑，此前法国和西班牙也报告了类似的结果，表明该地区可能出现衰退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/german-industry-unexpectedly-shrinks-amid-recession-threat</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 07:05:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于日本央行加息押注与美国就业形势谨慎，全球债券涨势陷入停滞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/global-bond-rally-stalls-as-japan-rout-meets-us-jobs-caution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四，在美国重要就业报告公布之前，全球债券的火爆涨势陷入停滞，日本债务暴跌加剧了国债交易员的紧张情绪，他们本来就担心收益率下降太多。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/global-bond-rally-stalls-as-japan-rout-meets-us-jobs-caution</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 06:16:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
