    <item>
      <title>交易员纷纷押注日本央行负利率即将结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/boj-rate-hike-bets-ramp-up-as-ueda-and-himino-spook-traders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在日本央行领导层发表评论后，交易员迅速加大押注，认为日本央行最早将于本月废除世界上最后一个负利率制度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-07/boj-rate-hike-bets-ramp-up-as-ueda-and-himino-spook-traders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 04:04:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本股市动荡，股市和国债下跌：市场结束</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/oil-sends-commodities-to-two-year-low-bonds-rally-markets-wrap</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于市场猜测日本央行将很快废除世界上最后一个负利率制度，欧洲股市下跌，债券收益率上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-06/oil-sends-commodities-to-two-year-low-bonds-rally-markets-wrap</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 06 Dec 2023 22:43:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
